// Vendored icon library manifest. The icons ARE the `*.svg` files beside this
// file; an icon needs no entry here to exist. An `icon` entry only attaches
// search metadata:
//
//   aliases    - alternate NAMES for the icon; ranked with near-id authority.
//   tags       - related words; ranked below names.
//   categories - a closed vocabulary used to filter, never to rank.
